<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Spruce Cliff</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Spruce Cliff, established in 1950, is a quaint and charming residential neighborhood in the South West quadrant of Calgary.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">An escarpment overlooking the Bow River below, the community in <span class="par-xl"> Spruce Cliff is fast becoming a hotspot for both young home buyers and investors alike given its affordable residential properties, wide well-planned streets, and immaculate greens.</span></p>
            <p class="par-lg">The annual Stampede Breakfast and the Calgary Greek Festival are two of the most popular recreational activities that are organized especially for the residents of Spruce Cliff.</p>
        </div>
